      <p>Use the registration code below to sign up:</p>

      <div class="code-box">{{code}}</div>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{registerUrl}}" class="cta-button">Register Now</a>
      </p>

      <p>If the button doesnâ€™t work, copy and paste this link in your browser:</p>
      <p>{{registerUrl}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Nine Technologies Inc. <br/>
      This code is valid until {{expiresAt}}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
